node.text:
This has easily become my LIFESTYLE. I’m grateful to be able to share my joy for it with you guys!

I started sports in the 7th Grade (basketball, volleyball, track) & played those sports all the way through college. Always played at a very high level , & being active was I knew! I find so much joy and excitement in competition & anything that’s going to challenge me! I may be small, but I can also be UNSTOPPABLE 🦾😈 #qimmahtherapy 

Shot by @nate_zielke_creates

node.text:
It’s a lifestyle to be Healthy Mentally for me. It has taken me such a long way. It’s been more valuable to work on my mental then my physical. But life is about balance, and it allows me to consider all aspects in my life that need work. The goal should be that Everything in your life should be “Healthy”. The mind is the only thing that can manifest that as your reality. If you don’t think it, or want it, or desire, or even believe in it, how can it be? Dream about it, pray on it, and most importantly.. LIVE IT. 💕 Every day, every step you take is one step closer. And it only gets easier.. once you recognize good, you start to feel good cause you realize THIS IS WHAT I NEED. This is what I’ve been yearning for. You’re so close, you’re right there, don’t give up. 🦾

🎥 @shotbysham

node.text:
Happy SPACE JAM FRIDAY 🏀 🐰!!

Stepped back on the court for the first time in a LONG time, and it felt SO GOOD! Reminded me how much love I had for the sport. 

My parents always told me , I was the only player who was ALWAYS smiling while I played. 😆 I was always having so much fun and I felt so alive when I was on the court. I felt fast and unstoppable!

Another great way to stay in shape effortlessly, and playing a sport you love and enjoy! I went up and down the court about 10 times and I was sweating like no other! Now that’s my kind of cardio 😍💨

@1stphorm #1stphorm

To #nationaldogday 😍 Before it’s too late, here are my little Angels 👼 !

I’ve had “Nugget” the red teacup poodle for over 4 years, she’s almost 5 years old! and she has been my everything, that’s my little mama . I love you Nugget, you’re smarter than you know, and the most loving Angel I could dream of! Yet she’s my little protector! GRRR!! 🐕 

And welcoming “Baby” the new member to the family. She is a teacup Yorki, with a beautiful white and black “Oreo” coat haha about 6 months old and she has brought so much Life and Responsibility to my little Family. Thank you for Challenging me and teaching me patience and LOVE. You’re the cutest little Muffin head, and you are the Perfect fit! (But no more peeing on the carpet) 😤 I’m done buying new ones! Haha Thank you for giving Nugget a little play buddy and being the best sister she could ask for. ☺️🥰🙈💕 I’m guna cry 🥺😅!

I LOVE DOGS. My favorite animal in the world!
